column5: Went to the Islands yesterday (1:30PM - 6:00PM) and only was able to hook into a small catfish.  Swpet my usual areas with both lures which have worked for my last two times I went (5 pike the first times, 3 pike the second time).  Pike gone for the summer?  Also, I was surprised that the catfish took a chomp at my xrap.
Your shallow shoreline spots are only good so long> Find some water exposed more to main Lake. They don't leave the Islands entirely.
I started working those deeper spots too.  I'm ging to focus on those spots entirely next time.
